 3A4 inhibitors.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/191000/', '', 'Lesinurad, Febuxostat, Pegloticase, Sulfinpyrazone, Rasburicase, Probenecid, Allopurinol', '', 1767369485);
